                                // `parse_option_contracts_v3` right-text arm
                                // already surfaces unknown text as
                                // `UnknownEnumVariant`, but this
                                // generator-emitted arm coalesced silently to
                                // `0` — masking schema drift on every wildcard
                                // tick parser with `contract_id = true`. Mirror
                                // the canonical strict-decode policy so a
                                // future server addition (e.g. binary options)
                                // fails loud at the boundary instead of
                                // corrupting downstream filters.
                                other => return Err(DecodeError::UnknownEnumVariant {
